    • Class Models.Data.SingleInstancedSerializable

      class SingleInstancedSerializable extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialization Methods

        • readObject
          public void readObject(ObjectInputStream ois) throws IOException, ClassNotFoundException
          Overrides Java Serializable readObject()
          Parameters:
          ois - ObjectInputStream
          Throws:
          IOException - If object was unable to be read
          ClassNotFoundException - If class was not found
        • readResolve
          public Object readResolve()
          Overrides Java Serializable readResolve to retrieve a single instance from DataStore ReferenceMap rather than creating new one, hence solving the de-sync problem from serializing/de-serializing classes into multiple data files

          UUID uuid
